@page "/greet/{name}"
@layout AppLayout
@authorize redirect="/welcome"
@title "Hello"
@description "A parameterized-route demo page (sign-in required, like all of Pulse)."
<section class="bz-hero"><h1>Hello, @name 👋</h1>
<p>A parameterized-route demo (/greet/{name}). Like every Pulse page it requires sign-in; MotoView's wildcard certified-query support (@@cacheable on a parameterized route) is demonstrated elsewhere, since nothing in Pulse is public.</p></section>
@code { }




